## Implementation Details

### Dynamic Font Size Preview

The preview section now dynamically applies the selected font size:

```tsx
style={{ 
  fontSize: accessibility.fontSize === "small" ? "12px" 
    : accessibility.fontSize === "medium" ? "14px" 
    : accessibility.fontSize === "large" ? "16px" 
    : "18px" 
}}
```

This shows users exactly how their chosen font size will look throughout the application.

### Contextual Feedback

Info boxes only display when their corresponding setting is active:

```tsx
{accessibility.highContrast && (
  <div className="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20">
    {/* Info content */}
  </div>
)}
```

This provides confirmation feedback without cluttering the interface.

---

## Enhancement Pattern

This enhancement demonstrates the pattern used in the Settings UI improvements:

1. **Replace Card Layout** - SettingsCard â†’ SettingsPanel
2. **Wrap Form Fields** - Direct input â†’ FormGroup wrapper
3. **Use Enhanced Components** - Basic input â†’ EnhancedSelect/AdvancedToggle
4. **Add Contextual Feedback** - Static â†’ Dynamic info boxes
5. **Improve Visual Hierarchy** - Better spacing and colors

